org.dmd.dmg
Interface DarkMatterGeneratorIF

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseDMWGenerator, BaseDMWGeneratorNew, BaseDMWGeneratorNewest, DmwDMWGenerator, DMWGenerator, DMWGeneratorOriginal
public interface DarkMatterGeneratorIF

The DarkMatterGeneratorIF interface must be implemented by classes that are referred to in Dark Matter Generator (DMG) configurations as objects that will generate code based on Dark Matter Schemas (DMS) or other kinds of configuration files.

void gatherUserInput(DmgConfigDMO config,
                     ConfigLocation loc,
                     ConfigFinder f,
                     SchemaManager sm)

Parameters:
config - The generator config.
loc - The location where the config was found. Code if often generated relative to this location.
f - The configuration finder
sm - The schema manager that contains the base schema plus any others that were requested in the .dmg config file via the schemaToLoad attribute.

setFileHeader
